*.log
*.rpt

# [INCLUDE: folders] allow hosting folders
!**/log/
!**/logs/
!**/report/
!**/reports/
!**/rpt/

# [INCLUDE: files in folders] re-include everything under them
!**/log/**
!**/logs/**
!**/report/**
!**/reports/**
!**/rpt/**
